node.text:
It has been the greatest honor of my life to fight for a country, and a man, that I love so much!

Proud of you @realdonaldtrump. You  work ethic is unrivaled! You have made our country strong. You have made our country proud! We love you! 🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸
